privateJob.title: Ultratech Cement Electrician Recruitment 2021, Apply Online for various vacancies in Haryana
privateJob.body:
Name of the Vacancies:

  •  Electrician

Description:

A new private job vacancy from Ultratech Cement has been published in Haryana for the post of Electrician. If you are looking for a job in Haryana, then this is an opportunity for you, you must have relevant skills to apply for these Vacancies in Electrician. If you are interested in these posts which have come out in Electrician, then check the details below, which include Rolls and Responsibility, Key Skills, Documents Required, etc.

Total vacancies:

  • Various vacancies have released.

Selection Process:

  • Online
  • Written test

Application fee:

  • No information is given about the application required.

Educational qualification:

The candidates who are interested to apply for the Ultratech Cement job must have the following qualification:

  • The candidates must have completed the 10th from a recognized board to apply for the application Ultratech Cement Electrician Recruitment 2021

Key skills required :

The candidates who are interested to apply in these job openings must have the following key skills that are required to do this:

  • You must have knowledge of electric materials.

Ultratech Cement Electrician PayScale :

  • The Payscale information will be decided at the time of the interview.

The document needs to be carried:

The candidates who will be selected for the interview must carry the below-mentioned documents:

  • The first and foremost thing is your resume/CV which has your educational background and other related information.
  • You must have your Adhaar card for identity purposes.
  • You must have other identity proofs like a PAN card, voter id, or Passport to prove your citizenship.
  • At last, you should have photocopies of important educational certificates.

How to apply for Ultratech Cement Electrician Recruitment 2021?

Candidates who are eligible and interested to apply for Ultratech Cement Job then you should follow the below steps to apply:

Note: You can also apply by clicking the apply now button shown above to apply directly from here

  • First of all, read the Ultratech Cement Electrician Recruitment 2021 notification thoroughly at the official website @Ultratechcement.com
  • You should have an email id and a phone number for communication purposes.
  • Click on the apply now link for the post you want to apply for.
  • Fill in the required details and submit.
  • Pay the application fee asked for.
  • Finally submit and download the application form for future purposes.
